==Hungarian==

===Etymology===
From the [[Hungarian]] word ''[[szultán]]'' which, directly translated into [[English]], means [[sultan]].
It has [[Turkish]] origins from the [[arabic]] term for [[monarch]].

===Proper noun===
'''Zoltán'''

# A [[Hungarian]] name meaning [[sultan]].

